room_title: Escape room "Escape the 90's" by EpIQ Escapes in Jackson (MI)
room_description: Re-enter the world of the 90s in this nostalgic rewind. It's NYE 1999 and the USA is on high alert in preparation for Y2K. When the ball drops in Times Square, the new Millennium will arrive and things are going to be ruined forever. Can you escape before the computers crash?
